<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两周后，双胞胎坐在树屋里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一只蜜蜂有多少个眼睛？”凯蒂问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂正在读一本关于蜜蜂的书。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊在给杰利刷毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“两个。”乔伊回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“五个。”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她翻了一页。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好。”她说，“蜜蜂一分钟扇动几次翅膀？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一千次？”乔伊猜道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一万两千次。”凯蒂告诉她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂躺下，想着蜜蜂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想象自己是只蜜蜂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是一只困倦的蜜蜂。”她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，她就开始做梦了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她是蜜蜂凯蒂，拍打着翅膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他蜜蜂在她身边飞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她能听到它们翅膀的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂！”乔伊大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂突然睁开了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的书页在风中翻动着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊站在窗边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰利不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天空变绿了。”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>空中布满了乌云。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂站起来看了看风向袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它在风中笔直地飞着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“暴风雨就要来了。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她听到隆隆的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雷声！我们走吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女孩们急忙走下了楼梯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！”乔伊喊道，“爷爷要把小鸡们赶进鸡圈里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女孩们跑过去帮忙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们追赶尖叫的小鸡们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“进去！”他们大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灰尘在空气中旋转。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“进去！“小鸡一只接一只地从鸡圈门跑了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“跑到房子里去。”爷爷叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我随后就进去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈在后门廊等着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“气象局发布了龙卷风警报。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把门打开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女孩们冲了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>厨房里的收音机播放着轻音乐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“龙卷风警报！”凯蒂大喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得当心！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她从门边的挂钩上拿下了组长帽子戴上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这家人准备好了！”她一边朝壁橱走一边说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她从架子上拿出一个盒子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把它拿到了厨房的桌子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“手电筒、急救箱、水、零食。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈，枕头和毯子准备好了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在这儿。”妈妈指着桌子下面的筐说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195421</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望爸爸能回家来。”乔伊担心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在爷爷打开纱门时，收音机里的音乐停了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>传出来一个播音员的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“国家气象局已经向布恩镇发出龙卷风警报。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>目前的强雷暴可能会引起龙卷风。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>警报中的城镇包括柳树溪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“龙卷风警报！”凯蒂大喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那意味着逃生！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去打开暴风雨避难所的门。”爷爷说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈拿起筐，凯蒂拿起了盒子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我拿收音机。”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>外面，大雨和冷风打在他们的脸上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天太黑了！”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸！”当爸爸的卡车加速驶上车道时，乔伊喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253678</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷打开通往暴风雨避难所的门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快点儿！”他大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“麦古！”凯蒂喊道，“快！狗狗！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她和狗狗冲进地下室的楼梯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“杰利在哪里？”乔伊大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈用胳膊搂住乔伊的肩膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，宝贝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在没时间找猫咪了。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，杰利......” 乔伊小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她和妈妈跟着凯蒂走下了楼梯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷跟在他们后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸关上避难所的门并锁紧了它。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麦古甩了甩皮毛上的水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈从篮子里拿起毯子和枕头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拿着这些。”她对双胞胎说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们能听到雨敲打避难所门的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂紧紧地抱着麦古。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>84</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊把枕头放在她的头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>85</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雷声响得越来越大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>86</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在他们上方，灯泡一闪一闪的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>87</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都抬头看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>88</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325606</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，灯就灭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>